%% ActivaClub - Remember Device Flow (AC-010)
%% Diagram 6 of 8
%% Last updated: 2026-04-05

sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant MembersLambda
    participant Cognito

    Note over User,Cognito: First login — user checks "Recordar este dispositivo"

    User->>Frontend: Check "Recordar este dispositivo por 30 días" + enter OTP
    Frontend->>MembersLambda: POST /v1/auth/verify-otp { email, session, otp, rememberDevice: true }
    MembersLambda->>Cognito: AdminRespondToAuthChallenge { EMAIL_OTP, session, otp }
    Cognito-->>MembersLambda: { AuthenticationResult: { AccessToken, IdToken, RefreshToken, DeviceKey, DeviceGroupKey } }
    MembersLambda->>Cognito: ConfirmDevice { DeviceKey, PasswordVerifier, DeviceGroupKey }
    Cognito-->>MembersLambda: OK (device remembered for 30 days)
    MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 200 { accessToken, idToken, refreshToken, deviceKey }
    Frontend->>Frontend: Store DeviceKey in localStorage
    Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to dashboard (role-based)

    Note over User,Cognito: Subsequent login from remembered device (< 30 days)

    User->>Frontend: Enter email + password on /login
    Frontend->>MembersLambda: POST /v1/auth/login { email, password, deviceKey: "<stored>" }
    MembersLambda->>Cognito: AdminInitiateAuth { USER_PASSWORD_AUTH, email, password, DEVICE_KEY }

    alt Device recognized and valid
        Cognito-->>MembersLambda: { ChallengeName: DEVICE_SRP_AUTH, Session }
        MembersLambda->>Cognito: AdminRespondToAuthChallenge { DEVICE_SRP_AUTH, SRP_A }
        Cognito-->>MembersLambda: { ChallengeName: DEVICE_PASSWORD_VERIFIER }
        MembersLambda->>Cognito: AdminRespondToAuthChallenge { DEVICE_PASSWORD_VERIFIER, verifier }
        Cognito-->>MembersLambda: { AuthenticationResult: tokens }
        MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 200 { accessToken, idToken, refreshToken } (no OTP required)
        Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to dashboard — OTP screen skipped
    else Device expired (> 30 days) or unknown
        Cognito-->>MembersLambda: { ChallengeName: EMAIL_OTP, Session }
        MembersLambda-->>Frontend: 200 { challengeName: EMAIL_OTP, session }
        Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to /verify-otp (normal OTP flow resumes)
    end
